{"tid":1405650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月5日全港被罷工","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T23:01:25.000Z","uid":39568,"like":338,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b6f6826ec41cf7ca7e5c651ca4073b468e3d32","tid":1405650,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">好多人都因為各種原因<br />\n唔能夠85罷工<br />\n佢地絕對需要<span style=\"color: red;\">被罷工</span><br />\n佢地都好為香港出一分力<br />\n各位連登仔/港鐵站車長站長<br />\n請幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n致各司機<br />\n堵塞各個主要交通幹道<br />\n屯門公路/大欖隧道/青馬大橋/獅子山隧道/大老山隧道/觀塘迴旋處/紅隧等等<br />\n各式各樣<span style=\"color: red;\">交通意外</span><br />\n請各位司機配合<br />\n真正全民大罷工！<br />\n8月5日香港需要你<br />\n<br />\n致港鐵車長站長<br />\n大圍/九龍塘/紅磡/調景嶺/金鐘/旺角/西鐵<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5:00</span>開始全民不合作運動<br />\n各連登仔幫忙<span style=\"color: red;\">接力</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用最少資源做到最大效益<br />\n港鐵快跑運動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">急停制/路軌/車長室/火警鐘撳手</span>等等<br />\n分3/4 team人可癱瘓一個上午</span><br />\n港鐵車長/站長可<span style=\"color: red;\">按章工作</span><br />\n幫幫忙盡量拖延時間<br />\n香港人需要你</span>"},{"pid":"a5d75c98ce6f96c64381ce1b8aaa0597377b4490","tid":1405650,"uid":39568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c7839520b55b94ab6a2641f2193291a2fec250b","tid":1405650,"uid":37746,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:41:20.000Z","msg":"拜託大家塞哂地鐵同巴士 塞到我地好多同事會罷工"},{"pid":"a8497e947ed28fb22f4f8708ca17cb08b83b9a4f","tid":1405650,"uid":241363,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:41:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n按章工作<br />\n利申港鐵站長"},{"pid":"2a6a2f9ad094c213fe7ff38f2826ac339d4c1493","tid":1405650,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor