月5日東鐵線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1407848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1407848</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8月5日全港被罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1405650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1405650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5e561651070a0688cd6cf1637d53ada6afa15911","tid":1405650,"uid":54613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:26:18.000Z","msg":"西鐵線聽日有不合作活動 大家留意<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1407725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1407725</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7d53403387c9b19c5e36d7cc2b399b0ec3b64b58","tid":1405650,"uid":180485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:26:33.000Z","msg":"大西北既牛牛全部同我入哂黎！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花］8月5朝早7點15元朗西鐵站要屯元天人！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391481</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKKTWDq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKKTWDq.png&h=017b10ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oR0G5wM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoR0G5wM.png&h=d8660f17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gRSm5wO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgRSm5wO.png&h=92e57ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/upiYoiu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FupiYoiu.png&h=7e8f5fa4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f199d0d296557905e2773fb16412e9248b8da2ff","tid":1405650,"uid":54613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3OBZSbU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OBZSbU.png&h=1e505c33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWwnPYz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWwnPYz.png&h=8b1624bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dg6yWDA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdg6yWDA.png&h=8d289229&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bce3a0fbb06b8e1d9975bbf1afc00de2f52c98e9","tid":1405650,"uid":227395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4b6f6826ec41cf7ca7e5c651ca4073b468e3d32","tid":1405650,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">好多人都因為各種原因<br />\n唔能夠85罷工<br />\n佢地絕對需要<span style=\"color: red;\">被罷工</span><br />\n佢地都好為香港出一分力<br />\n各位連登仔/港鐵站車長站長<br />\n請幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n致各司機<br />\n堵塞各個主要交通幹道<br />\n屯門公路/大欖隧道/青馬大橋/獅子山隧道/大老山隧道/觀塘迴旋處/紅隧等等<br />\n各式各樣<span style=\"color: red;\">交通意外</span><br />\n請各位司機配合<br />\n真正全民大罷工！<br />\n8月5日香港需要你<br />\n<br />\n致港鐵車長站長<br />\n大圍/九龍塘/紅磡/調景嶺/金鐘/旺角/西鐵<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5:00</span>開始全民不合作運動<br />\n各連登仔幫忙<span style=\"color: red;\">接力</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用最少資源做到最大效益<br />\n港鐵快跑運動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">急停制/路軌/車長室/火警鐘撳手</span>等等<br />\n分3/4 team人可癱瘓一個上午</span><br />\n港鐵車長/站長可<span style=\"color: red;\">按章工作</span><br />\n幫幫忙盡量拖延時間<br />\n香港人需要你</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"我正正係需要被罷工嘅一群！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果7：30am先開始不合作運動，我就一定要被迫上班<br />\n<br />\n但如果5:00開始不合作運動，我一定會企出嚟一齊幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信好多香港人同我一樣，都好想一齊罷工，但只係需要同伴齊上齊落先可以做到全城罷工<br />\n<br />\n希望聽朝5:00會見到大家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55125bd893bc8fc1fb21fcc4ac90316ce61067e","tid":1405650,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:30:14.000Z","msg":"<spa